{
  "stem": "1901.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 442.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, being Jewish and being in underground, and where can we go to?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have the right contacts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So how did it feel being sort of separated as being Jewish when it hadn't really been a part of your life up till then?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were not real-- we were not real separated with the-- what they've done in Holland, all the Jews outside of Amsterdam have to come to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed in our area because they were, more or less, it was more or less 50% Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the shops were closed for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We only could shop between 2:00 and 5:00.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the people very good to us in that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we had to wear our--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the shops there, they supplied everything what they had for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how can I say-- we didn't-- we were not sure of anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything what was required, we got from the shops.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So but we didn't-- how can I say-- we didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, food wise or anything or between 2:00 and 5:00 was not very important.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could buy our-- what we needed, we could buy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we couldn't go on the street after.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That became in '42-- we couldn't go on the street after 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was all-- all the time something more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "New regulations came up, all the time more regulations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, then, I-- yeah, we played amongst ourselves, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, we had some Jewish-- the Jews could go to certain establishments.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "May be danger, but you realize maybe danger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could have picked up the whole all in one go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how my father was picked up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was working somewhere in one of the suburbs outside, in a hall.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
